rcaCRelevantDirective: We do not distinguish between sensitive and less sensitive areas i DK. All areas are considered as sensitive and therefor the standards given in the legislation holds standards for all WWTP regardless of placement (but depending on size.The UWWT directive was implemented in april 1994 in Demark. The implementation relied partly on exsisting legislation and on a new act "Regulation an water water permmissions etc...". Regarding the effluent standards there was a possiblity to be granted an exemption untill december 1998 in the act.
